Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:03.77,RiskySubs,Dark!Kuromi,0,0,0,,You don't understand\Na single thing about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:05.31,RiskySubs,Dark!Kuromi,0,0,0,,You good-for-nothing friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:08.10,RiskySubs,Baku,0,0,0,,P-Please, Miss Kuromi,\Nyou have to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:10.31,RiskySubs,Gureco,0,0,0,,Ever since Kuromi changed like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:13.36,RiskySubs,Gureco,0,0,0,,she's turned half the world to darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:19.35,RiskySubs,Kooni,0,0,0,,Oni! Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:20.77,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,{\i1}My powers are restored,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:22.94,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,{\i1}but without MM, I can't become Nico again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:25.23,RiskySubs,Dark!Kuromi,0,0,0,,Begone with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:27.81,RiskySubs,Kooni,0,0,0,,Oni!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:29.02,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:29.56,RiskySubs,Dark!Kuromi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:30.65,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:31.73,RiskySubs,Kooni,0,0,0,,Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:33.44,RiskySubs,Friends,0,0,0,,There's two of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:37.10,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Stop muckin' up my world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:40.06,RiskySubs,Dark!Kuromi,0,0,0,,Tch. How'd you get out of the Dark World?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:43.23,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,The word "impossible" is not in my diary!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.40,RiskySubs,Baku/Collimo,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.44,RiskySubs,Baku,0,0,0,,The saying goes "dictionary!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:50.90,RiskySubs,Collimo,0,0,0,,Only the real Kuromi would\Nflub on a catchphrase like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:53.48,RiskySubs,Gureco,0,0,0,,Wow, Kuromi's just so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:57.77,RiskySubs,Dark!Kuromi,0,0,0,,You're getting along better than I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.77,0:00:58.77,RiskySubs,Dark!Kuromi,0,0,0,,I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:01.81,RiskySubs,Dark!Kuromi,0,0,0,,If you weren't here,\NI wouldn't be so sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:04.81,RiskySubs,Dark!Kuromi,0,0,0,,I'm gonna paint you in pure darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:06.27,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,I-I can't dodge that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:08.65,RiskySubs,Collimo,0,0,0,,You came in with a cool line\Nand {\i1}not{\i0} a plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:10.31,RiskySubs,Romina,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.81,0:01:14.90,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Huh? We're saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:18.68,RiskySubs,Romina,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll back you up from afar, Kuromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.23,Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(626,908)}Wanna know who I am? Check out the first season!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:20.40,RiskySubs,Dark!Kuromi,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:22.31,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Alright. No other choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:23.10,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:24.69,RiskySubs,Dark!Kuromi,0,0,0,,Not if I get you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:27.06,RiskySubs,MM,0,0,0,,{\i1}Universe!
